      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|>A break won't change anything. The deadlines are still there, the expectations are still there, and I'm still the same person who's failing at everything. It feels like a cycle that never stops. There's just no light at the end of this. It feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just... stop. Not just take a break, but stop everything.",
